Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:06.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來 人們就對妖怪心存畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:12.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而走在那眾妖之前 統領著百鬼夜行的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:16.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們稱其為妖怪的總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:18.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是如此稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魑魅魍魎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:23.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑頭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 奴良陸生現身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:12.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子絕不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:15.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你也這麼評價的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:21.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那說明我們沒有白來浮世繪町
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對方一葉障目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:28.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒意識到他們已經落入了我的手掌心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:33.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到何時才意識得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等意識到的時候已經遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:39.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還希望各位能繼續助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看好你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:41.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赴湯蹈火在所不辭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那將成為四國妖怪的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.90,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,300)}高貴之魂 燃於紅中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:06.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群傢伙終究是想毀滅奴良組吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:10.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組裡的人不斷被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:13.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:20.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅奴良組對四國妖怪來說真的是上策嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 從長計議的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:27.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不如來統治我們 讓我們成為他們的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:30.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼四國妖怪的真正企圖是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如牛鬼所說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:48.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們如果是要毀滅奴良組 那應該早就大規模動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們卻沒這樣做 這就說明他們另有所圖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:59.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須在加奈同學他們遭遇危險之前 迅速解決此事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 那個臭老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再碰見她 我要她好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好少主及時趕到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:13.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到少主竟然親自來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:23.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來少主果然很重視我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:28.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情真是舒暢啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:30.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也別太亂來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟已經上了年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:05.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清十字團 全體集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 各位來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:09.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:11.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮世繪町的地圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些叉叉又是什麼意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:20.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是根據本人的情報網做出的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:25.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些叉叉就是被不明人士破壞掉的神社和祠堂所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 神社和祠堂被破壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:32.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 最近連續出現這種事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:40.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說明了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這問題問得很沒水平 家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這當然都是妖怪幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…這會不會是酗酒的人幹的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:54.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要盡清十字團的全力來查出搗毀祠堂的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:57.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始調查 清十字團 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…現在就出發啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說大家等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在外面很危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:14.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那少主也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三羽鴉 青田坊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們當護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 清十字團的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一路順風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走啦 陸生媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:36.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 我們也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:42.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組裡出了這麼大的事 陸生卻要和朋友們出去玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也被毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:01.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮世繪町到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 看啊 看啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清十字團 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天白天的時候這裡還是好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是在夜晚被毀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:16.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:20.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近可能還潛伏著妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:22.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家分頭找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去對面看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 加奈也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學 我們也開始找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要找到妖怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及…及川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有必要躲起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就找這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:39.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祠堂開始腐朽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 土地神也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:47.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪所為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 他們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 看這布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是從衣服上掉下來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:05.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 難道在這裡KISS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們之間難道有一腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個角度看不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是四國妖怪幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:18.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為奴良同學和家長同學有一腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳踏兩隻船啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:25.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊少主 剛才的話可能被聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 這不是柚羅同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:33.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚羅同學 傷已經痊癒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:34.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴良同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:36.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時追兩隻兔子的結果是一隻兔子也抓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:42.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能小看兔子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚羅同學怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:05.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 不愧是奴良同學 找到妖怪的線索了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道是不是線索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:11.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給本人的情報網吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定查個水落石出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:32.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了…您到底在在意什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:36.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不覺得這裡有什麼好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:46.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一再這裡看守了200年了 卻從也沒聞過這種氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不應該有這種氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:58.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡確實有點怪 竟沒納豆的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:02.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的古怪不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地方以前可沒這麼暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:06.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人別想通過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:09.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比你更熟悉這山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總大將 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:50.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後過了300年 你已變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱神刑部狸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:56.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊 奴良組總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 數量真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:11.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前大概有一百零八尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:17.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是四國妖怪任俠總元締
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:22.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四國八十八鬼夜行的根據地 山口靈神堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 隱神刑部狸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:25.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:32.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元締 您和這老頭是老相識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和這孩子一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:39.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 稍等一下 很快就習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那不是座墊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:52.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:56.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多話要說 先來一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:57.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了好久 腳都走痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:15.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍後給你來個冷敷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島 該你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:23.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查找妖怪的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 發出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塗壁A
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:27.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生同學不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:50.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町內的神社和祠堂都被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組員也被襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之間有什麼關聯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您昨晚救我於水火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:33.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 昨晚毛倡妓被鉤針女襲擊 我趕了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於此同時 那個祠堂被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:40.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 毛倡妓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:46.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已知道了四國妖怪的企圖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家召集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分頭保護好尚未被破壞的神社和祠堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切不可擅離職守
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:02.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人或許會搞出些大動靜 但那只是調虎離山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:04.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調虎離山？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞出些大動靜 把我們引過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就會趁機實現自己的企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的企圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想動搖奴良組的地基
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:25.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神聚集了人們的信仰和「畏」 是組裡的根本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:32.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想除掉土地神 讓人們的信仰和「畏」轉向四國妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想從根本上弱化奴良組
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想支配的不只是奴良組甚至是更個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再讓他們如願了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:44.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:44.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:52.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 已經都佈置好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 接下來就是等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們隨便跑到這裡真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:27.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主的同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:30.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學 你應該看過地圖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:35.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:41.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將破壞事件的發生地點以及發生時間聯繫起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箭頭勾勒出了一個螺旋形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:48.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 箭頭所指的尚未被破壞的祠堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他們的下一個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:53.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:57.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要在這裡遇見妖怪 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 鉤針女出現在妖怪橫町了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然設法逃掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人開始調虎離山了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 某個祠堂快要被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:20.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個 青田坊聯繫說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學和…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:23.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學和島同學也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明跟他們說了多少次不要到外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:29.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:31.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎已經都解開了 島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於白天發現的那塊布的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已由四國的一位研究妖怪的教授發來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:37.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 四國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:43.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四國好像有個會吃衣袖的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袖捥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這妖怪好像很善於殺害土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:58.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神就是住在這種神社或祠堂中的土地守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又名產土神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:06.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此怪異的裝束…應該沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:10.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就是這祠堂土地神了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:14.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袖捥大人常常從背後偷襲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後會拉一下你的袖子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:20.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回頭看到了袖捥大人的臉 就會被詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:23.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是不想被詛咒就要老老實實地把袖子給他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:25.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要老實服從
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:27.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清…清…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 島同學 別拉我那裡啊 發不了帖了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清…清…清繼同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身…身後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:38.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身後？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不能往後看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你冷靜點啊 別來妨礙我 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學 拜託你啦 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:49.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 清繼同學就會被詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了 我還有這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:59.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-14日本代表之射門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的世界杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞啥啊 島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖…妖怪啊 剛才有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們把祠堂破壞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也是他們幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:28.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續觀察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:40.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險 冰麗 他們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是妖怪幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你殺害了土地神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:10.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:14.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在搞什麼 還不來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:15.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你過去的 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護袖捥大人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 請快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:34.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青田坊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就是之前那群烏鴉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:44.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我犬鳳凰既不會逃也不會躲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:45.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:48.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是你們做好覺悟才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再嘴硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:55.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的火焰是無敵的 燒死你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為灰燼 隨風飄散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:04.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 四國第一怪力的手洗鬼就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要比力量的話 我是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:14.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身披鐵青色袈裟的破戒僧 就是我青田坊大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:23.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 媽媽正忙呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:35.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在空中戰勝我 還早了一百年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:36.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞎扯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:43.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們連烤雞都不如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:45.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這火焰還真不好對付
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:49.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對自己的火焰過於自負
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:53.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本沒想到自己的招數已被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:57.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 正是這份傲慢會要了他的命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我來了結你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:10.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能被四國最華麗的妖怪犬鳳凰擊敗是你們的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:21.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:27.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我犬鳳凰竟會引火焚身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是被區區烏鴉幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:33.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的敗因是你的傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:37.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也配叫鳳凰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:40.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是條狗 連烤雞都算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:49.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再鬥下去也沒啥意思 下次再做了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:51.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:29.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 青田坊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 毛倡妓 竟然穿著水手服 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護少主 我特地從雪女那兒借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:34.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上說很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:36.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪種意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:38.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 滑頭鬼之孫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:40.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏實與千羽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
